videos.description: Badgers QB Jack Coan connects with Kendric Pryor for a 35-yard touchdown on the game's opening drive.
videos.headline: Coan hits Pryor for 35-yard Wisconsin TD

videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier throws an interception on his first pass of the game, leading to Jonathan Taylor's 7-yard touchdown run on the next play.
videos.headline: Rosier's INT leads to Taylor TD on next play

videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier scrambles out of the pocket and runs over a Badgers defender for a gain of 21 yards.
videos.headline: Miami QB Rosier runs over defender

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor breaks free for a 41-yard gain, setting up Alec Ingold for a Wisconsin touchdown.
videos.headline: Taylor's 41-yard run sets up Wisconsin TD

videos.description: QB Jack Coan tricks the defense on a play action, then rolls out into the end zone to put Wisconsin up 28-3.
videos.headline: QB Coan fools defense for another Wisconsin TD
